{"tid":1689912,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"平野鈴子捐10萬助612基金","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T10:41:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"717fe2596814469d306f19c2cfc62ccf7af4a1a9","tid":1689912,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/2B3PHERWW3HDRK7DVJGPO6KQ7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2F2B3PHERWW3HDRK7DVJGPO6KQ7A%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=1c48040a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2F2B3PHERWW3HDRK7DVJGPO6KQ7A%2F&h=bd156693\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/2B3PHERWW3HDRK7DVJGPO6KQ7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n平野鈴子捐10萬助612基金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日本人平野鈴子（圖）因聲援反送中運動聲名大噪，7月起在日本發起募款，她透過繙譯表示至今籌得約170萬日圓（折合約12.3萬元），第五度專程飛來港，今次捐出10萬元予612人道支援基金。平野早前動用籌得資金與多名在日港人成立團體「Stand with Hong Kong at Japan」發起在日聲援行動。<br />\n<br />\n平野透過繙譯暨Stand with Hong Kong at Japan核心成員之一William指，一直以來是用平野鈴子個人名義發起眾籌，她有朋友被捕後獲得612基金支援，加上612基金滿10萬元才公開捐款人身份，欲藉此表達她對香港的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/RODdnFL0PrwH1DdplV3H5f6dnr0=/802x1397/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/W3U46D6UUOTFEBLDKEZL2JOPJE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FRODdnFL0PrwH1DdplV3H5f6dnr0%3D%2F802x1397%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FW3U46D6UUOTFEBLDKEZL2JOPJE.gif&h=59d41d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在日港人成立組織辦活動<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：保時捷播《榮光》警強拖司機落車㩒地押走<br />\n<br />\n另一名核心成員Yurble稱，Stand with Hong Kong at Japan上月初成立，現時有約70名成員，平野以代表及中間人形式給予意見及聯繫當地日本人做宣傳。日本另一邊廂也有無組織港人辦聲援香港抗爭行動，他們會盡量避開以免活動相撞。<br />\n<br />\n對於平野被指主張日本極右及軍國主義，與港人抗爭追求人權民主自由相違背，William引述平野表示她不是極右主義及軍國主義者，只去過靖國神社做義工打掃，是出於愛國，又指日後不會再發表與日本政治相關的言論。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁楚雙"},{"pid":"e85ef6900a747f6615b117b3e7380e678f2b6635","tid":1689912,"uid":88578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"多謝外國勢力支持"},{"pid":"26b39e39d923a0afe561a65bc4cec5b39fd0dbcb","tid":1689912,"uid":284592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e91d284f0631dde64c8e5c4ba10fe3faf57837","tid":1689912,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"捐612<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659f4af1b136d049e9228ef6149256d377a84516","tid":1689912,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:25:25.000Z","msg":"我希望612 同星火都可以批多少少錢比每個被捕人士<br />\n<br />\n睇完612個report都係大約每人7千到<br />\n<br />\n大佬個個出黎比人一捉 部電話就無撚硬 比人扣起 有撚排先拎得返<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘又爛埋眼鏡呀 其他野<br />\n<br />\n你批得7千 跟本買iphone都剩係買到舊款機<br />\n<br />\n如果D手足係比較新款少少既機, 7千蚊仲要倒蝕出黎<br />\n<br />\n在職人士就話自己再um兩三千出黎就話姐<br />\n<br />\n但學生辛苦做完PT買新電話 跟住又比人捉撚左 電話又要貼錢再買好撚慘。人地仲要比班狗凌虐, 你批多少少都得掛。唔好咁孤寒啦屌"},{"pid":"119f33b792d80665c3ba19a1804617ddc2035524","tid":1689912,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:44:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05f6c8adb43e23ef6733e0261f21c4b2f37e630f","tid":1689912,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f